ZH: 我们公司经常有外国客户来访。
EN: Our company often has foreign customers come to visit.

ZH: 昨天有一位老朋友来访我家。
EN: Yesterday, an old friend came to visit my home.

ZH: 他们一行人来访了我们学校。
EN: Their group came to visit our school.

ZH: 我们应该让来访的客人感到宾至如归。
EN: We should make the visiting guests feel welcome.

ZH: 他们是特地从国外来访的。
EN: They came specifically from abroad to visit.

ZH: 明天我们要去看望来访的客户。
EN: We will go visit the client who is coming tomorrow.

ZH: 他们的来访给我们带来了很大的惊喜。
EN: Their visit brought us a lot of surprises.

ZH: 那些来访的学者将会与我们做学术交流。
EN: The visiting scholars will engage in academic exchanges with us.

ZH: 我们邀请了一位专家来访讨论这个课题。
EN: We invited an expert to come discuss this topic.

ZH: 昨晚我受到了一位老朋友的来访。
EN: Last night I received a visit from an old friend.

ZH: 她打电话提前告知她即将来访。
EN: She called in advance to inform us of her upcoming visit.

ZH: 来访的外交官将会进一步商讨合作事宜。
EN: The visiting diplomat will further discuss cooperation matters.

ZH: 学校领导为来访的家长们安排了接待仪式。
EN: The school leaders arranged a reception ceremony for the visiting parents.

ZH: 我们需要设计一个行程表来安排来访的日程。
EN: We need to design an itinerary to arrange the visit schedule.

ZH: 来访的委员会对我们的工作给予了高度评价。
EN: The visiting committee gave high praise to our work.

ZH: 我们正在准备迎接即将到来的来访团队。
EN: We are preparing to welcome the upcoming visiting team.

ZH: 来访的专家带来了一些新的观点和经验。
EN: The visiting experts brought some new perspectives and experiences.

ZH: 我们公司会安排带领客户参观工厂的行程。
EN: Our company will arrange a factory tour for the visiting clients.

ZH: 来访的大使将会与政府官员进行会面。
EN: The visiting ambassador will meet with government officials.

ZH: 让我们一起为来访的客人准备一顿丰盛的晚餐。
EN: Let's prepare a sumptuous dinner for the visiting guests.
